public class AttributionMap
extends org.apache.commons.collections15.map.LazyMap<java.lang.String,java.util.List<java.util.List<Attribution>>>

This is a nested collection view of an AdverseEventReport, exposing the various attributions in a way that's friendly to the form view and the data binder. It's a map of lists of lists. The keys/indices are

  • The attribution key (from the constants in ExpeditedAdverseEventInputCommand)
  • The adverse event index (relative to the AE report)
  • The cause (study agent, concomitant medication, disease, etc.) index within the AE
